title: A1466 820-3209 solved thank you.
message: hi friends , the fan want it to spin just a little almost nothing I check for bad probe points and I find some bad looking around U7600 , I find out path was gone between C7604 and U7600 , U7600 i think create [SIZE=12px][FONT=Courier][FONT=Courier]=PPCPUVCCIO_S0_REG [/FONT][/FONT][/SIZE]so i guess fan will not spin without that rail , i rebuild the path with a wire and machine power on and works great thank you!
